description:
Social Media has taken the world by storm. Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, Twitter, Tumblr, Snapchat, Youtube, Messenger, LinkedIn and many others are now household names. How did we survive before without all those forms of social media? How much time are we spending on social media? And what is its impact on our lives? Im Gary Kent, join me as we navigate through this amazing digital world with Dr. Arlene Taylor.

=== CHAPTERS ===
00:00 Intro
00:22 The history and rise of Social Media
02:49 The impact of Social Media on the society
05:19 Social Media integrated into our lives
08:37 Upside of Social Media
09:58 Downside of Social Media
18:54 The disappearing skill to communicate
23:03 Useful advice on how to improve our communication skills
23:21 Biblical encouragement to learn positive communication
26:01 FREE BOOKLET: Media and the Brain by Scott Ritsema
27:28 Closing prayer
